PhillipWidgets
==============

A collection of HTML/AJAX widgets that directly bind to your database model, 
so you don't need implement database query/update in your code, it just work out of the box.


HOW TO USE

* Checkbox : Auto update database model
  Ex:
    <%= phillip_checkbox("user",user.id,"active") %>
    
    => Display a checkbox that reflect the status of the current user, if unchecked it will update the active field of users table as FALSE.

* radio button...(coming soon)



